data.description: WELCOME HOME TO YOUR COMPLETELY REMODELED LAKE HOME! Right under 1600 Sq.Ft., this beautiful home not only has a spacious back porch but also is complete with a Private enclosed Hot Tub House 20' from the water. Get ready for your weekend escape you and your family have searched for. This 4 bedroom, 2 bath home has new carpet, new paint throughout, 2 new barn doors, new fixtures, hardware, granite, ceiling fans, appliances and landscape. Home is easily energy efficient as you are able to enjoy the attic fan to cool the home all year long. With almost half an acre to enjoy you can sip your coffee or sweet tea while watching some of the most beautiful Texas sunsets. The neighbors are family and cant wait for you to arrive. Seller is motivated to sell so we hope you enjoy making this your favorite getaway.
